<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF716ACEF7EE9CE217B3B0F3" pageId="138" pageNumber="898" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF716ACEF7EE9CE217B3B0F3" blockId="138.[2064,2659,2585,3009]" pageId="138" pageNumber="898">
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF716ACEF7EE9CE216F4B1E6" box="[2066,2292,2747,2772]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Kerivoula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="138" pageNumber="898" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="titania">Kerivoula titania</taxonomicName>
appears to be sister to 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF716ACEF7EE9C871695B1C9" authorityName="G. S. Miller" authorityYear="1898" box="[2066,2197,2782,2811]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Kerivoula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="138" pageNumber="898" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="minuta">K. minuta</taxonomicName>
, and this clade is sister to the rest of the 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF716ACEF7869D5316FBB011" authorityName="Horsfield" authorityYear="1824" box="[2170,2299,2826,2851]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Vespertilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="138" pageNumber="898" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="hardwickii">hardwickii</taxonomicName>
species group, although it might also be related to 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF716ACEF6569D73145BB079" authorityName="Hill &amp; Francis" authorityYear="1984" box="[2474,2651,2858,2891]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Kerivoula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="138" pageNumber="898" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="intermedia">K. intermedia</taxonomicName>
. Specimens previously attributed to K. fitania from Hainan and 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFF716ACEF6AC9D2117B0B0AB" box="[2384,2480,2936,2969]" name="Taiwan" pageId="138" pageNumber="898">Taiwan</collectingCountry>
islands now represent 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF716ACEF7639DFD170AB0F3" box="[2207,2314,2980,3009]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Kerivoula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="138" pageNumber="898" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="furva">K. furva</taxonomicName>
. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
